Package com.mongodb.client.model.search

Interface NumberRangeSearchOperatorBase

All Known Subinterfaces:
NumberRangeSearchOperator
@Sealed @Beta(CLIENT) public interface NumberRangeSearchOperatorBase
A base for a NumberRangeSearchOperator which allows creating instances of this operator. This interface is a technicality and does not represent a meaningful element of the full-text search query syntax.
Since:
4.7
See Also:
  • SearchOperator.numberRange(FieldSearchPath, FieldSearchPath...)
